  "dct_description_sm": [
    "Argentina Social Census Data, 2001 is a polygon theme representing Departmentos (3rd level administrative units) in Argentina as of 2001. Attribute data include summary results of the 2001 Argentinan census questions regarding occupational and workplace characteristics. The documentation of these variables can be found in the \"Social\" section from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Argentina 2001 Census collection."
